Introduction

We will present life expectancy over time in a set of countries using gapminder data imported from https://raw.githubusercontent.com/resbaz/r-novice-gapminder-files/master/data/gapminder-FiveYearData.csv.

Plot of data

Here is a plot of life expectancy over time

p<- ggplot(data, aes(x=year,y=lifeExp), colour=continent)
p<- p + geom_line(aes(group=country)) + geom_point(alpha=0.2) 
p  + facet_wrap(~continent)
